SYNOPSIS
    format_opt_lists.pl : --doom=DOOM : [--help -? --usage] [--man]
    [--stuff=STUFF] : [--help -? --usage] [--man] --doom=DOOM
    [--stuff=STUFF]

DESCRIPTION
    Make sure format strings %a, %r and %o expand properly.

OPTIONS
    --help -? --usage
        Display the usage message and exit

    --man
        Display man page

    --doom
    --stuff

